value.name: Capt John Adolph Flemer (1859-1957) - Find a Grave Memorial
value.snippet: Capt. John Flemer, 98, of Oak Grove, VA, former Coast and Geodetic Survey officer, died Wed. at the home of his daughter, Mrs. James LaTane. A funeral service was held Sat. at st. Peter's church, with burial in the familly cemetery at Ingleside.

value.name: Adolph C. Flemmer Obituary
value.snippet: Adolph “Al” C. Flemmer, age 95, passed away Saturday morning, September 17, 2022 at Bay Shores Nursing Center after a brief illness. He was born April 10, 1927 in Akaska, South Dakota to the late John J. and Christine Flemmer. He enlisted in the United States Coast Guard and served during World War II.
